snippet.title: Army Men - Game  Release Trailer (1998)
snippet.description:
Army Men -  Game Trailer.
Developed  by The 3DO Company
Published in USA  by The 3DO Company (Published in Europe by Ubi Soft) for PC (Windows) in 1998
System : PC (Windows). A Game Boy Color Version was ported in 2000 by Digital Eclipse Software.
Year : 1998 

Trailer found on the 'Might&Magic VI : The Mandate of Heaven' ' game disc.
